fields.name: CacheDuration
fields.description: The duration for which the content needs to be cached. Allowed format is in ISO 8601 format (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601#Durations). HTTP requires the value to be no more than a year

fields.name: DynamicCompression
fields.description: Whether to use dynamic compression for cached content

fields.name: QueryParameterStripDirective
fields.description: Treatment of URL query terms when forming the cache key.

fields.name: QueryParameters
fields.description: query parameters to include or exclude (comma separated).
